Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:10.06,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The cloudless, blue sky is so dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:14.28,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Today I'll tell you my feelings once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:19.46,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Today is the first step for the bashful you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:23.94,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The warmth of your hand makes me feel secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:28.75,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Don't worry... There's nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:33.59,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Trust me... Look only at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:40.55,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Our feelings intertwine and a fire is lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:45.86,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}We met each other in this wide, wide world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:50.22,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}because we are bound by the thread of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:52.59,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}We'll be together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:55.38,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}From now on till forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.38,0:23:00.21,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I want to remain like this for just a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:05.92,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Every time we touch, my heart skips a beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:14.02,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I think of you more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:22.52,English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I want you so much I could melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Víš jak chutná víno?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Napij se závanu jeho vůně, poválej ji na jazýčku a polkni doušek po doušku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.35,0:23:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
